            "title": "車cam直擊｜油塘13歲男學生過斑馬線遭校巴撞倒 網民嬲爆：呢啲司機唔可以放過",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/d0f1e30ffb3571efbfbb4177d1c10102/815c7209a4aa4eb6a8c30ab783adfe6f-39349d71152dc22d0847fc15544024a4-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67cabdaeabac5\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67cabdaeabac7\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/f6d530aa2b9086c7fec6ba97b46aafc9/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250307/_2025030717295217603.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>油塘今日（7日）發生一宗交通意外，一名13歲男學生於斑馬線遭一輛駛至的校巴撞倒，幸手腳擦損，在場接受治理後毋須送院。有網民上載一條拍攝到整個意外過程的車CAM片段至社交平台，片中見到校巴駛至斑馬線未有停車，右邊車頭直撞男學生，令他跌倒地上。\n\n</p>\n<p>事件發生於中午12時許，一輛校巴沿茶果嶺道往鯉魚門方向行駛，至高輝道一個斑馬線過路處時，撞到一名過路的13歲男學生。男學生手腳擦損，在場接受治理後毋須送院，警方正調查意外原因。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4124618/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"一名13歲男學生於斑馬線過馬路。網上片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/149d77e8a887f18435086da3f0c8198e/2025-03/AQOMLC2EO2VE7BQ3Fqe2jfew6R5XVRx7YR2OWYrW1h42e85G5ZRVYRBrIm01YneeFh1raJerp9Pvdbl2WDqo-SYQ_mp4_snapshot_00_04_493.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一名13歲男學生於斑馬線過馬路。網上片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4124617/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"校巴的車速不算快，惟駛至斑馬線未有停車。網上片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/13ccdcf8d4de9b1f5c1372a509913be1/2025-03/AQOMLC2EO2VE7BQ3Fqe2jfew6R5XVRx7YR2OWYrW1h42e85G5ZRVYRBrIm01YneeFh1raJerp9Pvdbl2WDqo-SYQ_mp4_snapshot_00_05_215.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        校巴的車速不算快，惟駛至斑馬線未有停車。網上片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4124616/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"校巴右邊車頭直撞男學生，令他跌倒地上。網上片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ded9910e67d18ee24265dad7f71acead/2025-03/AQOMLC2EO2VE7BQ3Fqe2jfew6R5XVRx7YR2OWYrW1h42e85G5ZRVYRBrIm01YneeFh1raJerp9Pvdbl2WDqo-SYQ_mp4_snapshot_00_05_605.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        校巴右邊車頭直撞男學生，令他跌倒地上。網上片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4124615/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"校巴右邊車頭直撞男學生，令他跌倒地上。網上片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/87a580829069915f0b68df0820993009/2025-03/AQOMLC2EO2VE7BQ3Fqe2jfew6R5XVRx7YR2OWYrW1h42e85G5ZRVYRBrIm01YneeFh1raJerp9Pvdbl2WDqo-SYQ_mp4_snapshot_00_05_851.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        校巴右邊車頭直撞男學生，令他跌倒地上。網上片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4124614/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"校巴右邊車頭直撞男學生，令他跌倒地上。網上片段截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8b61c4239a4e8c74f3130b331f719f2e/2025-03/AQOMLC2EO2VE7BQ3Fqe2jfew6R5XVRx7YR2OWYrW1h42e85G5ZRVYRBrIm01YneeFh1raJerp9Pvdbl2WDqo-SYQ_mp4_snapshot_00_06_566.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        校巴右邊車頭直撞男學生，令他跌倒地上。網上片段截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>片中見到校巴的車速不算快，惟駛至斑馬線未有停車，右邊車頭直撞男學生，令他跌倒地上。\n\n</p>\n<p>大批網民表示，校巴司機未有留意路面情況，「好多司機真係當這些斑馬綫無到」、「行人以為個個司機都識停，但好多都係盲嘅直過」、「呢啲司機唔可以放過，佢仲要揸校巴，唔止危及路人，成車學生條命喺佢手」。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
